Package:        nqrustbackup-database-common
Architecture:   any
Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Depends:        nqrustbackup-common (= ${binary:Version}), nqrustbackup-database-postgresql (= ${binary:Version}), dbconfig-common, lsb-base (>= 3.2-13), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - common catalog files
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides generic abstraction libs and files to connect the NQRustBackup
 Director daemon to a database.


Package:        nqrustbackup-database-postgresql
Architecture:   any
Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Depends:        dbconfig-pgsql | dbconfig-no-thanks, lsb-base (>= 3.2-13), postgresql-client, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests:       postgresql
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - PostgreSQL backend
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides the functionality to connect the NQRustBackup Director
 daemon to a PostgreSQL database.


Package:        nqrustbackup-database-tools
Architecture:   any
Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Depends:        nqrustbackup-common (= ${binary:Version}), nqrustbackup-database-common (= ${binary:Version}), lsb-base (>= 3.2-13), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts:      bacula-sd-mysql, bacula-sd-pgsql, bacula-sd-sqlite3
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - database tools
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides tools that requires access to the NQRustBackup database.
